---
title: Pork Sausages & Cherry Tomato Traybake with Gravy & Parsley
description: Sausages and veggies, it’s a classic we can all get behind. You’ll be running to line up for a serving when you know that these veggies are roasted with balsamic blistered cherry tomatoes and spices. Make sure to pour over the gravy to seal the deal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
